Title: Enter the Void
Writer: Gaspar Noé, Lucile Hadzihalilovic (with the help of)
Actors: Paz de la Huerta, Nathaniel Brown, Cyril Roy, Olly Alexander
Plot: An American drug dealer living in Tokyo is betrayed by his best friend and killed in a drug deal. His soul, observing the repercussions of his death, seeks resurrection.
Production: Eurimages, Les Cinémas de la Zone, BUF, Filmförderungsanstalt, Orange Cinéma Séries, Filmarto, Wild Bunch, Canal+, Fidélité Films, Essential Filmproduktion GmbH, Ministère de la Culture et de la Communication, BIM Distribuzione
